import React, { useState } from 'react';
import { Tabs, Tab, Form, Button } from 'react-bootstrap'

function Search() {
    return (
        <Tabs defaultActiveKey="artista" id="uncontrolled-tab-example">
            <Tab eventKey="artista" title="Artista">
                <Form>
                    <Form.Group>
                        <Form.Label>Buscar por artista</Form.Label>
                        <Form.Control placeholder="Digite o nome do artista" />
                    </Form.Group>
                    <Button type="submit">Buscar</Button>
                </Form>
            </Tab>
            <Tab eventKey="album" title="Album">
                <Form>
                    <Form.Group>
                        <Form.Label>Buscar por album</Form.Label>
                        <Form.Control placeholder="Digite o nome do album" />
                    </Form.Group>
                    <Button type="submit">Buscar</Button>
                </Form> 
            </Tab>
        </Tabs>
    );
}

export default Search;
